              <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                <path d="M21 15a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H7l-4 4V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h14a2 2 0 0 1 2 2z"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="resource-card-title" id="res-shout-title">Shout Text Service</h3>
              <p class="resource-card-type">Text support — Free, 24/7</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="resource-card-desc">If you're struggling but don't feel able to talk, text SHOUT to 85258. Shout's trained crisis volunteers offer confidential text-based support for anyone in crisis — available any time, entirely free.</p>
          <div class="resource-card-actions">
            <div class="btn btn--sm" style="background-color: #c62828; color: white; border: none; cursor: default;" aria-label="Text SHOUT to 85258">
              <svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M21 15a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H7l-4 4V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h14a2 2 0 0 1 2 2z"/></svg>
              Text SHOUT to 85258
            </div>
            <a href="https://giveusashout.org" class="btn btn--outline btn--sm" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" aria-label="Visit Shout website (opens in new tab)">More info</a>
          </div>
        </article>

      </div><!-- /grid-3 -->
    </div>
  </section>

