              <p class="resource-card-type">Online CBT — Free via NHS</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="resource-card-desc">SilverCloud offers clinically validated, structured online cognitive behavioural therapy (CBT) programmes for anxiety, depression, stress, and sleep difficulties. Available free to NHS staff — no GP referral required, available 24/7.</p>
          <div class="resource-card-actions">
            <a href="https://www.silvercloudhealth.com/uk" class="btn btn--primary btn--sm" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" aria-label="Visit SilverCloud website (opens in new tab)">
              Access SilverCloud
              <svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M18 13v6a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V8a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h6"/><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"/><line x1="10" y1="14" x2="21" y2="3"/></svg>
