            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="resource-card-title" id="res-cameron-title">Cameron Fund</h3>
              <p class="resource-card-type">Financial assistance — Grants &amp; loans</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="resource-card-desc">The Cameron Fund has provided financial assistance to GPs and their families since 1970. The Fund offers grants and interest-free loans to registered GPs in financial difficulty due to illness, mental health problems, family breakdown, or other hardship. The application process is means-tested and completely confidential — there is no contact with employers or the GMC.</p>
          <div class="resource-card-actions">
            <a href="https://www.cameronfund.org.uk" class="btn btn--primary btn--sm" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" aria-label="Visit Cameron Fund website (opens in new tab)">
              Visit Cameron Fund
              <svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M18 13v6a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V8a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h6"/><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"/><line x1="10" y1="14" x2="21" y2="3"/></svg>
            </a>
          </div>
        </article>

        <!-- BMA Benevolent Fund -->
        <article class="resource-card" aria-labelledby="res-bma-ben-title">
          <div class="resource-card-header">
            <div class="resource-card-logo" aria-hidden="true">
              <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--colour-primary)" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                <rect x="2" y="3" width="20" height="14" rx="2" ry="2"/><line x1="8" y1="21" x2="16" y2="21"/><line x1="12" y1="17" x2="12" y2="21"/>
