          <p class="resource-card-desc">The BMA Benevolent Fund provides financial assistance and welfare support to BMA members and their dependants who are facing hardship. This can include help with living costs, disability adaptations, or other one-off financial pressures. Applications are assessed with compassion and discretion.</p>
