            <a href="https://www.bma.org.uk/advice-and-support/your-wellbeing/financial-and-legal-support" class="btn btn--primary btn--sm" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" aria-label="Visit BMA financial support page (opens in new tab)">
